I made a deal with Hartmann to pay half, $1.5 million, at the beginning of the summer and the other half at the end of the summer when I was done fishing.
By the end of that first summer I owned the boat outright."
But how could a boy have a half a million to pay out in a boat when he had just finished primary school?
I had saved up and put money aside, I had been working with my dad at sea when I was a boy, I fished with him every summer and got my share.
