Axel was born in Ísafjörður, where all his mother's family is from, but he has lived in Kópavogur since he was a boy.
I can fish here on the west coast because I have a permanent address with my grandmother in Ísafjörður.
I learned about these areas out west from rowing with my dad.
I move between fjords depending on how I feel, because this fishing area covers all of the Westfjords.
